trailingComments.value:
*
	 * The luminance texture.
	 *
	 * If `colorOutput` is enabled, the scenes colors will multiplied by their
	 * respective luminance values and stored as RGB. Luminance will be stored
	 * as alpha.

	 * @type {Texture}
